cf.Field.ancillary_variables¶

Field.ancillary_variables¶

A cf.AncillaryVariables object containing CF ancillary data.

Examples: 
>>> f.ancillary_variables
[<CF Field: specific_humidity standard_error(time(12)) g/g>]
